{"tid":1860984,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中旅巴士新增3條深圳灣往香港路線 多區都有上落客站","createTime":"2020-02-04T02:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:56:31.000Z","uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0657ae5dcbd3291e083029e76279c992c91466","tid":1860984,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506490_1_20200204100443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506490_1_20200204100443.jpg&h=ad7a5390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府昨日宣布關閉多4個口岸，包括羅湖、落馬洲、皇崗、港澳碼頭口岸，凌晨起生效。旅客仍可經機場、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋及啟德郵輪碼頭出入境。<br />\n<br />\n中旅巴士在<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">微博</span></span></strong>公布，因應新的口岸安排，調整跨境巴士服務，新增3條由深圳灣口岸直達香港市區路線，往返港九新界，分別在上環、灣仔、太子、屯門及荃灣都有上落客站，每15至30分鐘一班，中旅巴士指，有關安排是要滿足廣大群眾的跨境出行需求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506490-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506490-20200204.htm&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=0dcbcbd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506490-20200204.htm&h=093af0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506490-20200204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港中旅汽車服務有限公司（China Travel Tours Transportation Services H.K. Ltd）係香港一間跨境客運公司，係香港交易所上市公司－<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港中旅國際投資成員</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2597%2585%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=a2ccfe98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99</a><br />\n<br />\n香港中旅國際投資有限公司 (港交所：308) 是一家在香港交易所上市的綜合企業公司。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由香港中旅集團控股，持有 55.04%股權，香港中旅集團是中國國資委管理的大型企業集團，是中國最大的旅遊產業集團。</span></span></strong>主要業務是客運服務（包括：香港中旅汽車服務、噴射飛航），景區業務，貨運及運輸業務，酒店業務，旅遊及相關業務，高爾夫球會所業務，發電業務，投資控股及其他。 公司在香港註冊，董事局主席為張學武。2004年純利為HKD 901,654,000 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=032854f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港中旅汽車服務有限公司 <br />\n網站 <a href=\"https://www.hkctsbus.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctsbus.com%2F&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=d3b9f1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctsbus.com/</a>"},{"pid":"8ad9447568e4388a20729598992958e750d9ffa9","tid":1860984,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"真係唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7edbe8d93fc275542e96e145db589483d23702","tid":1860984,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad9447568e4388a20729598992958e750d9ffa9","tid":1860984,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"真係唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" c